<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.4.4">
<l>tuṇiviṉi yuṉakkuc colluvaṉ maṉamē</l>
<l>toḻuteḻu toṇṭarkaḷ tamakku</l>
<l>piṇiyoḻit tamararp peruvicum paruḷum</l>
<l>pēraru ḷāḷaṉem perumāṉ</l>
<l>aṇimalark kuḻalā rarampaiyar tukilu</l>
<l>māramum vārivan taṇinīr</l>
<l>maṇikoḻit tiḻinta kaṅkaiyiṉ karaimēl</l>
<l>vatariyāc ciramat tuḷḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Oh, heart, I now speak to you confidently. Our great lord,</l>
<l rend="indent">the great gracious one who,</l>
<l>Removing the bonds of devotees who begin worshipping [him],</l>
<l rend="indent">grants [them] the great heaven of the immortals,</l>
<l>He is the one in Badarī Āśrama on the banks of the Ganges</l>
<l rend="indent">where lovely waters descend, casting up jewels,</l>
<l>Sweeping along sandal paste and clothes of celestial maids</l>
<l rend="indent">with curls full of ornate blossoms.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
